Choice Lots
for your new home
✔
Buy a share in our community for the low price of
$48,000
and you can have your choice of one of the many lots sprinkled throughout Bradenton Tropical Palms for the price of your share.
✔
Your low share price includes your lot, plus
water, lawn service, twice a week garbage pickup, and all the park amenities, such as our large heated pool and hot tub.  It also includes use of our three indoor air conditioned pickle ball courts, our championship shuffle courts, plus our fitness center and library. The many social activities include bingo, euchre, hand and foot, dances, a jam session every Friday, golf, pickle ball, and shuffle leagues, plus many holiday and dinner parties .
​
✔
Our present monthly maintenance fee is only
$210
*
.  There is no mortgage on the community and we have a substantial reserve fund built up so there is little chance of any extra assessments.
*
Fees may vary slightly from year to year depending on the community operating budget.
We also have some of the homes listed below available for rent on a yearly basis.  The monthly rent is from $1,100 and up.
To find out more click here
